    {
      "id": "EternaCityCondominiums4F_Text_IveHadThisTMRecycleForSuchALongTimeNow",
      "en_US": [
        "I’ve had this TM Recycle for such\n",
        "a long time now.\r",
        "It’s not anything that I have much\n",
        "use for these days.\r",
        "I do hope you’ll put it to good\n",
        "use, young Trainer."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "EternaCityCondominiums4F_Text_FolksLikeMeHaveALongHistoryWeCanLookBackOn",
      "en_US": [
        "Folks like me have a long history\n",
        "we can look back on.\r",
        "Young people like you have only the\n",
        "future to look forward to."
      ]
    }
  ]
}
